.4441 68.1681 78.1742 76.1384C72.5949 83.2311 69.7169 93.1 69.6202 105.471L69.6199 105.5L69.6202 105.529C69.7169 117.9 72.5949 127.769 78.1742 134.862C84.4441 142.832 93.777 146.916 105.914 147H105.962C116.753 146.925 124.358 144.1 130.624 137.84C138.822 129.65 138.575 119.385 135.873 113.083C133.934 108.564 130.239 104.893 125.185 102.469ZM106.555 119.985C102.042 120.239 97.3533 118.213 97.1221 113.874C96.9507 110.657 99.4116 107.067 106.832 106.64C107.682 106.591 108.516 106.567 109.335 106.567C112.03 106.567 114.552 106.829 116.844 107.33C115.989 118.008 110.974 119.742 106.555 119.985Z' fill='#BAC2CE'></path></svg></div></a><a href='https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite?url=https%3A%2F%2Feasterling-ms-newsletter.beehiiv.com%2Fp%2Fnew-post' target='_blank'><div style='max-width:28px;'><svg fill='none' height='100%' viewBox='0 0 211 211' width='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><circle cx='105.5' cy='105.5' fill-opacity='0.15' fill='#9CA3AF' r='105.5'></circle><path d='M82.1892 75.4698C82.1892 80.1362 78.526 83.8026 73.8638 83.8026C69.2015 83.8026 65.5383 80.1362 65.5383 75.4698C65.5383 70.8034 69.2015 67.137 73.8638 67.137C78.526 67.137 82.1892 70.8034 82.1892 75.4698ZM82.1892 90.4689H65.5383V143.799H82.1892V90.4689ZM108.831 90.4689H92.1797V143.799H108.831V115.801C108.831 100.135 128.812 98.8017 128.812 115.801V143.799H145.463V110.134C145.463 83.8026 115.824 84.8026 108.831 97.8018V90.4689Z' fill='#BAC2CE'></path></svg></div></a></div></div></div><div id='content-blocks'><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"></p></div><div id=\"the-builder-log\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:16px;\"><h1 style=\"color:#2A2A2A;font-family:'Trebuchet MS','Lucida Grande',Tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.75;margin:0;text-align:left;\">The Builder Log</h1></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"><b>Issue #002 — Launching on My Own Domain</b><br><b>March 13, 2026</b><br>By <b>Tony Easterling</b></p></div><div style=\"font-size:0px;line-height:0px;padding:30px 0px 30px;\"><div style=\"margin: 0 auto; border-top: 3px solid #030712; width:50%;\"></div></div><div id=\"owning-the-infrastructure\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:16px;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2A2A2A;font-family:'Trebuchet MS','Lucida Grande',Tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;margin:0;text-align:left;\">Owning the Infrastructure</h2></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> This week marked a milestone that feels small on the surface but important behind the scenes. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> The website is now live on <b>my own domain</b>. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> No platforms in the middle.<br>No shared infrastructure. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> Just something I built and control. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> Owning your infrastructure changes how everything connects. The website, the blog, and this newsletter are now all part of the same system. That means every project I build moving forward feeds back into the same place. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> Small steps, but the foundation matters. </p></div><div style=\"font-size:0px;line-height:0px;padding:30px 0px 30px;\"><div style=\"margin: 0 auto; border-top: 3px solid #030712; width:50%;\"></div></div><div id=\"mind-mark-closed-testing\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:16px;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2A2A2A;font-family:'Trebuchet MS','Lucida Grande',Tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;margin:0;text-align:left;\">MindMark — Closed Testing</h2></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> MindMark is the first app moving toward real users. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> It’s a private journaling app designed to remove friction from reflection. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> No social feed.<br>No noise.<br>Just a clean place to think. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> I’m opening a <b>small closed testing group</b> to help refine the experience before a wider release. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> If you’re someone who journals, tracks ideas, or just enjoys testing new tools early, I’d love your feedback. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> Early testers will help shape the direction of the app before it launches publicly. </p></div><div style=\"font-size:0px;line-height:0px;padding:30px 0px 30px;\"><div style=\"margin: 0 auto; border-top: 3px solid #030712; width:50%;\"></div></div><div id=\"a-question-for-creators\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:16px;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2A2A2A;font-family:'Trebuchet MS','Lucida Grande',Tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;margin:0;text-align:left;\">A Question for Creators</h2></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> Another project I’ve been experimenting with behind the scenes is a set of <b>LoFi creator tools</b>. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> These tools help automate parts of the process for generating long-form LoFi videos and loops without heavy editing workflows. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> Before I go deeper into developing these tools, I’m curious about something: </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"><b>Would creators actually want these tools if they were available on the Microsoft Store?</b></p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> If you’re a creator working with video loops or LoFi content, I’d be interested in hearing your thoughts. </p></div><div style=\"font-size:0px;line-height:0px;padding:30px 0px 30px;\"><div style=\"margin: 0 auto; border-top: 3px solid #030712; width:50%;\"></div></div><div id=\"this-weeks-insight\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:16px;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2A2A2A;font-family:'Trebuchet MS','Lucida Grande',Tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;margin:0;text-align:left;\">This Week’s Insight</h2></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> Progress compounds when the foundation is in place. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> The domain is live.<br>The newsletter is running.<br>Projects are moving forward. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> Once the infrastructure exists, every step after that becomes easier. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"> The goal now is simple: <b>keep shipping.</b></p></div><div style=\"font-size:0px;line-height:0px;padding:30px 0px 30px;\"><div style=\"margin: 0 auto; border-top: 3px solid #030712; width:50%;\"></div></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;text-align:left;\"><b>— Tony</b></p></div></div></div></div></div></body></html>"
