.4689Z' fill='#BAC2CE'></path></svg></div></a></div></div></div><div id='content-blocks'><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;text-align:left;\"> This week I stopped overthinking and just shipped. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;text-align:left;\"> The website is live.<br>The apps are moving forward.<br>The systems are forming. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;text-align:left;\"><b>Key idea</b></p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;text-align:left;\"><b>Progress compounds faster than polish.</b> Working beats perfect, every time. </p></div><div id=\"what-im-building\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:16px;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2A2A2A;font-family:'Trebuchet MS','Lucida Grande',Tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;line-height:36px;margin:0;text-align:left;\">What I’m building</h2></div><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:37px;padding-right:27px;padding-top:12px;\"><ul style=\"color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;list-style-type:disc;margin:0px 0px 0px 25px;padding:0;\"><li style=\"margin:10px 0px 0px 0px;\"><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><b>MindMark</b> — private journaling with gentle reflection </p></li><li style=\"margin:10px 0px 0px 0px;\"><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><b>BreathMark</b> — tactical calm for high-stress days </p></li><li style=\"margin:10px 0px 0px 0px;\"><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><b>DroneDash</b> — simple physics, clean gameplay </p></li></ul></div><div id=\"this-weeks-insight\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:16px;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2A2A2A;font-family:'Trebuchet MS','Lucida Grande',Tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;line-height:36px;margin:0;text-align:left;\">This week’s insight</h2></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;text-align:left;\"> If you automate the boring parts, you free energy for creativity. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;text-align:left;\"> AI isn’t replacing effort. It’s reducing friction — and friction is what kills momentum. </p></div><div id=\"tool-im-testing\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:16px;\"><h2 style=\"color:#2A2A2A;font-family:'Trebuchet MS','Lucida Grande',Tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;line-height:36px;margin:0;text-align:left;\">Tool I’m testing</h2></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;text-align:left;\"> CapCut for long-loop LoFi automation while I refine my own internal tool. Sometimes the right move isn’t building the tool yet — it’s shipping with what works now. </p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;text-align:left;\"><b>Tony</b></p></div><style>\n  p span[style*=\"font-size\"] { line-height: 1.6; }\n</style><div style=\"padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:12px;\"><p style=\"color:#2D2D2D;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;text-align:left;\"> Building systems that compound. </p></div></div></div></div></div></body></html>"
    }
  ]
}
